# HTML structure & semantics

Static single-page app. Markup in `index.html`; styles in `styles/main.css`; behavior in `scripts/`.

## Document skeleton

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Product Switcher</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="top-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">...</nav>
  <main class="card">...</main>
  <!-- scripts: gsap CDN → logo-animation.js → main.js -->
</body>
</html>
```

## Landmark regions

| Region | Element | Notes |
|--------|---------|-------|
| Global nav | `<nav class="top-nav">` | Fixed 32px; not inside `<main>` |
| Primary content | `<main class="card">` | White rounded card |
| Product media | `#centralArea` | JS injects video or fallback |
| Product details | `<aside class="info-left">` | Contains sole `<h1>` |
| Commerce | `<aside class="info-right">` | Price + CTA |
| Variant picker | `#switcher` | `role="tablist"`; tabs built in JS |

## BEM blocks (do not break)

- `top-nav` → `__group`, `__item`, `__logo`, `__logo-tagline`
- `card` — layout container
- `central-area` — media viewport
- `info-left` / `info-right` — product copy
- `switcher` → `__thumb`, `__inner` (+ `.active` on thumb)

Logo SVG internal classes: `logo-hook`, `logo-mark`, `logo-mark-inner`, `logo-bar`, `logo-accent`, `logo-glow-group`.

## Dynamic vs static markup

**Keep in HTML:** nav structure, logo SVG, info-left/right static copy, empty `#centralArea` and `#switcher`.

**Build in JS:** switcher thumbs, video element, fallback color div.

## Semantic rules

- One `<h1>` per page (product name in info-left).
- Interactive controls → `<button type="button">`; decorative labels → `<span>`.
- Decorative SVG/tagline → `aria-hidden="true"`.
- Switcher thumbs → `role="tab"`, `aria-selected`, `aria-label="Variant N"`.

## CSS file organization

- All component styles in `styles/main.css` until file exceeds ~400 lines.
- Future split: `styles/nav.css`, `styles/switcher.css`, `styles/card.css` — mirror BEM blocks.
- No inline `<style>` in index.html except critical above-the-fold if ever needed.

## Script load order

1. `gsap.min.js` (CDN)
2. `scripts/logo-animation.js` — exposes `window.ProductSwitcherLogo`
3. `scripts/main.js` — switcher, video, boot

Do not reorder without updating `feature-integrator` checklist.
